overview: Timpson The Musical is about the formation of a dynasty, a tale of love and loss, and a tale of shoes and tiny saws (keys). The Montashoes and the Keypulets hate each other, but a love between their children, Monty and Keeleigh, seeks to bring them together. But this isn’t just a rehash of Romeo and Juliet, it’s actually a lot closer to Airplane! and the movies of Mel Brooks.
title: Timpson: The Musical
